# API Test Scenarios – DummyJSON

Base URL: https://dummyjson.com

## TS_API_01 – Verify Login API with Valid Credentials
Endpoint:
POST /auth/login

Request:
- username
- password

Expected Result:
- Status code should be 200
- Token should be generated

---

## TS_API_02 – Verify Login API with Invalid Credentials
Expected Result:
- Status code should be 400
- Error message should be returned

---

## TS_API_03 – Get Product List
Endpoint:
GET /products

Expected Result:
- Status code 200
- Product list should be returned

---

## TS_API_04 – Create Order (Mock)
Endpoint:
POST /carts/add

Expected Result:
- Status code 200
- Order ID should be generated
